hopobject.body: We're at university together healthfundit.com Running for New York City comptroller lets Spitzer remind voters of what they really admired about him in the first place. He can return to the days of those long investigations he took the public on in years past, culminating with dates under the bright lights of television cameras regaling viewers with stories of vanquishing scoundrels for their benefit. If he is successful and the fire is rekindled, there is no telling where Spitzer might land. Gracie Mansion might be a nice place to get things back on track.
